title: Stanley Easy Home Plumbing Repairs (2015).pdf Gooner
description:
Publisher: Taunton Press; Spi edition (February 10, 2015)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1627109854
ISBN-13: 978-1627109857

Easy Home Plumbing Repairs is a concise, highly visual ready reference to the most common plumbing repairs that homeowners might tackle themselves.  The projects include everything from clearing a clogged sink to repairing (or replacing) various styles of faucets and fixing a running toilet.  With quick tips on tools and materials, this handy reference provides all you need to know to do your own plumbing repairs
